                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7513" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HRM-0509</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2484 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">汇“智”于光，融“机”于人 ——南京城市照明集团的智能机器协同发展之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Light Into Intelligence: The Way of Technological Intelligence Synergy for Nanjing Urban Lighting Construction and Operation Group  </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">张戌凡，周路路，张晓东，封思贤，臧锋</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南京师范大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南京市城市照明建设运营集团有限责任公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">能源工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人机协作；技术接受；南京照明集团；2023百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">human-machine cooperation; Technology acceptance; Nanjing Lighting Group</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“碳达峰、碳中和”对我国照明行业提出了高质量发展的必然要求。而物联网等新兴信息技术的普及，为当今智慧城市建设中照明资源的智能化带来了全新的机遇和挑战。南京市照明集团积极谋求智能化转型，以技术变革为主线，以智能信息系统赋能智慧路灯、助力智慧城市。本案例主要描述了南京城市照明建设集团奥南运维养护所，作为智能化转型的先行示范区，在其过程中所遭遇的技术接纳阻力与人机团队冲突。同时重点阐述了奥南运维所如何重塑人机协作团队的工作设计，进而助力采纳新技术后的人机协作新工作模式扎实落地。本案例旨在为以技术为主线的传统企业，在采纳新技术后高效发展人机协作、充分利用人机潜能提供参考，帮助学生理解人机协作等相关理论要点。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The concept of &quot;carbon peak&quot; and &quot;carbon neutral&quot; has presented a pressing demand for the lighting industry in China to pursue high-quality development. The flourishing of the Internet of Things and other emerging technologies offer new opportunities and challenges for the intellectualization of lighting resources in the construction of smart cities today. Nanjing Lighting Group is proactively pursuing intelligent transformation that prioritizes technological advancements and utilizes intelligent information systems to facilitate the growth of smart streetlights and cities. This case narrates how Nanjing City Lighting Construction Group&#39;s Aonan Operation and Maintenance Institute, a leading demonstration area for smart transformation, faced the the resistance to technology acceptance and human-machine conflicts during their efforts towards transformation. The focus of the case lies in how the Aonan Institute restructured its team in the context of human-machine collaboration to facilitate technology adoption and integration after transformation. The case is designed to serve as a reference for traditional companies that have adopted a technology-driven focus, to emphasize the importance of human-machine collaboration and help students better understand the theoretical underpinnings of such collaboration and associated issues.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《管理学》、《人力资源管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人机协作视角下的团队技术采纳；人机团队工作重塑；社会技术系统协同发展等相关的理论知识</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-09</td>
                            </tr>
